---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Button from "@/composables/buttons/Button.astro";
---

<Layout title='Web Applications | Qora Digital Agency'>
  <main class='bg-white'>
    <section class='container mx-auto px-8 py-16 md:py-24'>
      <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center'>
        <h1
          class='text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6'
          data-aos='fade-up'
          data-aos-duration='800'
        >
          Web Application Development
        </h1>
        <p
          class='text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12'
          data-aos='fade-up'
          data-aos-delay='200'
          data-aos-duration='800'
        >
          We build powerful, scalable web applications that transform your
          business processes and enhance user experiences.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16'>
        <article
          class='bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8'
          data-aos='fade-up'
          data-aos-delay='400'
        >
          <img
            src='/web-development/responsive.png'
            alt='SaaS Development'
            class='w-full h-48 sm:h-56 md:h-48 lg:h-56 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6'
          />
          <h3 class='text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4'>
            Responsive Design
          </h3>
          <p class='text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600'>
            Your software will not only look amazing, but it will also work
            perfectly on any device. We design intuitive experiences that keep
            users connected and satisfied, optimizing every interaction for
            success.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article
          class='bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8'
          data-aos='fade-up'
          data-aos-delay='600'
        >
          <img
            src='/web-development/security.png'
            alt='Analytics Integration'
            class='w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6'
          />
          <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>Security and Scalability</h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600'>
            We protect your application with advanced security standards and
            build an architecture ready to grow with your business. Whether you
            handle thousands or millions of users, you'll have reliable and
            efficient software.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article
          class='bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8'
          data-aos='fade-up'
          data-aos-delay='800'
        >
          <img
            src='/web-development/supabase.jpg'
            alt='Payment Integration'
            class='w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-6'
          />

          <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>
            Custom Integrations & Features
          </h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600'>
            We connect your software with the tools you need: payment systems,
            CRMs, advanced APIs, and more. We create unique solutions that solve
            your specific problems and differentiate you from the competition.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <section class='mt-24'>
        <h2
          class='text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16'
          data-aos='fade-up'
        >
          Featured Projects
        </h2>
        <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12'>
          <div
            class='project-card bg-white rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(8,_112,_184,_0.1)] hover:scale-[1.03] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100'
            data-aos='fade-right'
            data-aos-delay='200'
          >
            <div class='overflow-hidden rounded-xl mb-6 group'>
              <a
                href='https://app.primefit.coach'
                target='_blank'
                rel='noopener noreferrer'
              >
                <img
                  src='/web-development/projects/saas.png'
                  alt='SaaS Platform'
                  class='w-full h-64 object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500'
                />
              </a>
            </div>
            <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>Enterprise SaaS Platform</h3>
            <p
              class='text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors duration-300'
            >
              Scalable B2B solution handling 1k+ daily users with real-time
              analytics and reporting.
            </p>
            <Button link='https://app.primefit.coach' openTab={true} />
          </div>

          <div
            class='project-card bg-white rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(8,_112,_184,_0.1)] hover:scale-[1.03] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100'
            data-aos='fade-up'
            data-aos-delay='400'
          >
            <div class='overflow-hidden rounded-xl mb-6 group'>
              <a
                href='https://lumma-nine.vercel.app/dashboard'
                target='_blank'
                rel='noopener noreferrer'
              >
                <img
                  src='/web-development/projects/dashboard.png'
                  alt='Analytics Dashboard'
                  class='w-full h-64 object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500'
                />
              </a>
            </div>
            <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>Analytics Dashboard</h3>
            <p
              class='text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors duration-300'
            >
              Custom analytics platform with interactive visualizations and
              predictive insights.
            </p>
            <Button
              link='https://lumma-nine.vercel.app/dashboard'
              openTab={true}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class='mt-24 bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl p-12' data-aos='fade-up'>
        <h2 class='text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12'>
          Development Process
        </h2>
        <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8'>
          <div class='text-center' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='200'>
            <div class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>01. Planning</div>
            <p class='text-gray-600'>
              Detailed requirements analysis and robust system architecture
              design. We work closely with stakeholders to understand business
              goals and technical constraints.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='text-center' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='400'>
            <div class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>02. Development</div>
            <p class='text-gray-600'>
              Modern agile development with automated CI/CD pipelines and code
              quality checks. Our team follows best practices and uses
              cutting-edge technologies to deliver scalable solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='text-center' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='600'>
            <div class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>03. Testing</div>
            <p class='text-gray-600'>
              Rigorous quality assurance including penetration testing and
              performance benchmarking. We ensure security, reliability, and
              optimal performance across all devices and platforms.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='text-center' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='800'>
            <div class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>04. Deployment</div>
            <p class='text-gray-600'>
              Production deployment with 24/7 monitoring and proactive
              maintenance. We provide continuous support, updates, and
              optimization to ensure your application runs smoothly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
